RelatedSentence: In addition to raising her two daughters , Jeanie worked as a teacher , a day care provider , assistant manager for Pizza Hut , and most recently at the Osage City Library .
She leaves her loving memories to be cherished by her husband , Brooke , of the home : two daughters , Jennifer J. Lamond , Tulsa , Okla .
